                      <desc>Columetric layout of text: <locus target="#126v" facs="131">fol. 126v</locus> <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur#Ps150"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT2000Mazmur#Ps150</span></ref>;
                      <locus target="#136v #137r #137v" facs="141 142">136v, 137r, 137v</locus> <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1566hababa#ThreeYouths3"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT1566hababa#ThreeYouths3</span></ref></desc>
