                        <decoNote xml:id="b1">Parchment, 191 x 135 x 60 mm, four Coptic chain stitches attached with bridle attachments to rough-hewn boards of the traditional wood, covered with tooled leather, with decorative linen patches visible between the turn-ins, headband and tailband.</decoNote>
